title: Experience Hendrix - San Francisco (Live 2CD 3rd Show)2004 ak320
description:
Experience Hendrix - San Francisco (Live 2-CD 3rd Show)2004 ak320

The Experience Hendrix Tour is a unique opportunity for fans to experience the music and legacy of Jimi Hendrix in a way that CDs simply cannot offer,” explains Janie Hendrix, President & CEO of Experience Hendrix, L.L.C. “We felt strongly that a live presentation of the music that Jimi Hendrix created and which inspired him would be an exciting and unique way of conveying his relevance to today’s audiences.

This Show at The Warfield, San Francisco, CA, 2004
